<br>
How do I pay for it? <br>
<br>
One dual/tri/quadd kite of HG's in Rathe Mtns will pay for 8 to 20 hours of manaskin protection. In might take you 30 mins to totally transit, kill, egress from Rathe. Do it early in the morning or at off peak times in Rathe. <br>
<br>
Alternatively, I used porting money for peridots. Got 100pp for a DL TL last night while LFG in Velks. Right there is another 20 hours of protection. <br>
<br>
The bottom line is that it's relatively cheap protection. <br>
<br>
BUT...hehe...it has made me change my thoughts on the effect on our epic. I think the FREE aspect of the 800HP damage shield is indeed the perfect effect. There really is nothing better suited to our class. I can see many instances where a quick right click and refresh on the shield would be invaluable.<br>
